==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsolder
<hw>Un*sol"der</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>solder</ets>.]</ety> <def>To separate or disunite,
as what has been soldered; hence, to divide; to sunder.</def>
<altsp>[Formerly written also <asp>unsoder</asp>.]</altsp>
<rj><au>Tennyson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsoldiered</ent>⟦br⟧
